Class TableColumnExtractionRule

    public class TableColumnExtractionRule
extends AbstractChangeableEntity
implements java.io.Serializable
    Entity class for Table column extraction rule used for storing all the table extraction details like column start coordinate, column end coordinate, column pattern etc. defined for a particular table.
